main event: Three lights were observed in the sky near Manchester, Tennessee that traveled at high speeds and were visible for about 5 seconds.
interesting points: The lights looked like the size of navigation lights on a large transport, but moved much too fast to be a transport.
The witness said the phenomenon changed the perception of his eyesight that day and the object was moving.
The report states the observation could have been caused by the moon and certain well-known celestial phenomena.
The witness described the object as being about the size of large transport navigation lights at 10,000 feet.
The object appeared to be self-luminous, glowing, and changing color from red to yellow.
photographs: yes, the report includes a photograph of lights
